game.name: Princess Mermaid Mommy Birth
game.description:
Oh! The lovely mermaid princess Ariel looks pretty excited to get her first baby. It seems that she just went into labor so it is important to call 911 and take care of her until the ambulance reaches her home. Does not look pretty challenging and exciting? Join Princess Mermaid Mommy Birth and be prepared to become her doula for the day! The best part is that you would find all the needful and important items around her. Try to relax her in this medical simulation game as fast as you can!

Your first job in this one of the best doctor games is to pick up the phone and dial for the instant medical help. Till the time she is waiting for the ambulance to come, make sure to pack her bag with all the useful medical and daily life items. Do not forget to call her love to kiss on her forehead to make her feel happy. Keep her hydrating with a glass of water and oxygen so that she continues breathing until she reaches to the hospital! When she is in the operation theatre, make sure to have a safe delivery of her beautiful baby. 

Clean the body of her baby and use a pair of scissors to cut the umbilical cord in this HTML5 girls game! Check out the weight of her baby and put some baby powder on the body of little one! Make sure to put on some fresh diapers and help this new mommy to get some pills to relax her pain and recover after this painful journey. Use the towel to wrap up the baby and then breastfeed baby in a friendly environment! Provide her all the needful medical assistance she needs to enjoy a safe pregnancy experience! Check out more pregnancy games for girls that you can enjoy on multiple devices, no download required!
